---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import Navbar from '@/components/global/header/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/global/Footer.astro';
import Reveal from '@/components/widgets/Reveal.astro';
import { generatePaths } from '@/lib/utils/i18nUtils';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return generatePaths();
}

const shareLinks = [
  { label: 'Facebook', icon: 'lucide:facebook' },
  { label: 'X', icon: 'lucide:twitter' },
  { label: 'LinkedIn', icon: 'lucide:linkedin' },
  { label: 'Vimeo', icon: 'lucide:video' },
];

const selectorList = [
  'Type selector (e.g p, span, etc.)',
  'Class selector (e.g .element, .sidebar, etc.)',
  'ID selector (e.g #header)',
];

const tags = ['Blog', 'Creative', 'Portfolio', 'Theme', 'WordPress'];

const comments = [
  {
    author: 'By James Taylor',
    date: 'January 2, 2024',
    body: "I love this theme. Sometimes it's difficult to work with some themes, because even if they are created with Elementor, you can't edit all the things with Elementor.",
  },
  {
    author: 'By Oliver Williams',
    date: 'January 2, 2024',
    body: 'They have really taken their time to work on the appearance of the theme, also, they have a very interactive client assistance service, I like it!',
  },
];
---

<Layout title="Control your online banking while earning rewards — Zylo Blog" description="Resources article from Zylo on online banking, rewards, and modern product engineering.">
  <Navbar />

  <main id="main" class="pt-24 md:pt-[120px] pb-24 bg-surface-soft">
    <div class="container-page max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      {/* 1. Header */}
      <Reveal class="mb-10">
        <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand hover:underline mb-6">
          <Icon name="lucide:arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4" /> Back to blog
        </a>
        <span class="inline-block border border-hairline bg-canvas px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-ink uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 shadow-[var(--shadow-subtle)]">
          Resources
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-ink font-heading tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Control your online banking while earning rewards.
        </h1>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 2. Author + share */}
      <Reveal delay={80} class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-6 pb-8 border-b border-hairline">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center font-semibold font-heading text-xl">
              R
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink font-heading">Richard</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone">Community Organiser</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            {shareLinks.map((s) => (
              <a
                href="#"
                aria-label={s.label}
                class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-hairline bg-canvas text-steel hover:border-brand/40 hover:text-brand transition-colors"
              >
                <Icon name={s.icon} class="w-4 h-4" />
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 3. Article body */}
      <Reveal delay={120} class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-8 md:p-12 shadow-[var(--shadow-subtle)] text-steel leading-relaxed text-base mb-12">
        <p class="mb-6">
          We love to bring designs to life as a developer, and I aim to do this using whatever front end tools
          are necessary. My preferred tools are more modern javascript libraries like React.js but I like to use
          whatever is best for the websites needs. There are several reasons why a business would consider
          a rebrand and it doesn&rsquo;t necessarily mean the business has been unsuccessful.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-10">
          But in order that you may see whence all this born error of those who accuse pleasure and praise
          pain, I will open the whole matter, and explain the very things which were said by that discoverer of
          truth and, as it were, the architect of a happy life.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink font-heading mb-4">Using a Query</h2>
        <p class="mb-10">
          We love to bring designs to life as a developer, and I aim to do this using whatever front end tools are
          necessary. My preferred tools are more modern javascript libraries like React.js but I like to use
          whatever is best for the websites needs. There are several reasons why a business would consider a
          rebrand and it doesn&rsquo;t necessarily mean the business has been unsuccessful.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-10">
          Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus enim. In aliquam tempus porta. Mauris vel finibus risus.
          Maecenas egestas mi sed neque finibus, nec faucibus ipsum aliquet. Duis scelerisque at odio vel
          tempus. Morbi a tincidunt nunc, id rutrum erat. Fusce egestas quam vel facilisis tempor. Morbi non
          orci elementum, sollicitudin mauris laoreet, luctus est. Donec in mi lorem.
        </p>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-10">
          <Icon name="lucide:quote" class="w-10 h-10 text-brand flex-none" />
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <blockquote class="text-ink text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold font-heading leading-snug tracking-tight">
              &ldquo;Success is the result of perfection, hard work, learning from failure, loyalty, &amp;
              persistence&rdquo;
            </blockquote>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone">Phil Martinez</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mb-10">
          Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus enim. In aliquam tempus porta. Mauris vel finibus risus.
          Maecenas egestas mi sed neque finibus, nec faucibus ipsum aliquet. Duis scelerisque at odio vel
          tempus. Morbi a tincidunt nunc, id rutrum erat. Fusce egestas quam vel facilisis tempor. Morbi non
          orci elementum, sollicitudin mauris laoreet, luctus est. Donec in mi lorem.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink font-heading mb-4">On the specificity of selectors</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          The specificity of the : <span class="text-brand font-semibold">not()</span> pseudo-class is the
          specificity of its argument. The :not() pseudo-class does not add to the selector specificity, unlike
          other pseudo-classes.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6">
          The <span class="text-brand font-semibold">simple selector</span> that:
          <span class="text-brand font-semibold">not()</span> takes as an argument can be any of the following:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 mb-10">
          {selectorList.map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <Icon name="lucide:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand mt-1 flex-none" />
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <Icon name="lucide:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand mt-1 flex-none" />
            <span>
              Pseudo-class selector e.g: <span class="text-brand font-semibold">first-child, :last-of-type</span>
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-surface-soft p-6 md:p-8 font-mono text-sm text-steel mb-10">
          <div>{'li:not(.old)::after {'}</div>
          <div class="pl-8 my-2">
            <div>{'content: "New!";'}</div>
            <div>{'color: deepPink;'}</div>
          </div>
          <div>{'}'}</div>
        </div>

        <p>
          The specificity of the : <span class="text-brand font-semibold">not()</span> pseudo-class is the
          specificity of its argument. The :not() pseudo-class does not add to the selector specificity, unlike
          other pseudo-classes.
        </p>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 4. Tags */}
      <Reveal delay={140} class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-sm">
          <span class="font-semibold text-ink mr-1">Tagged with:</span>
          {tags.map((t) => (
            <a
              href="#"
              class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-hairline bg-canvas text-steel hover:border-brand/40 hover:text-brand transition-colors"
            >
              {t}
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 5. About Author */}
      <Reveal delay={160} class="mb-12">
        <div class="rounded-lg bg-canvas-dark p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start gap-6 text-center sm:text-left">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 flex-none rounded-full bg-primary text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center font-semibold font-heading text-2xl">
            PB
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-stone tracking-wide">About Author</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-on-dark font-heading mt-1">Peter Bowman</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-on-dark-muted text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
              Phasellus et ipsum justo. Aenean fringilla a fermentum mauris non venenatis. Praesent at nulla
              aliquam ligula.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-start gap-4 mt-1 text-stone">
              {shareLinks.map((s) => (
                <a href="#" aria-label={s.label} class="hover:text-on-dark transition-colors">
                  <Icon name={s.icon} class="w-4 h-4" />
                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 6. Next Post */}
      <Reveal delay={180} class="mb-12">
        <a
          href="/article"
          class="group block rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-8 shadow-[var(--shadow-subtle)] hover:border-brand/40 hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-subtle)] transition-all"
        >
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-brand uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">
            Next Post <Icon name="lucide:arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4" />
          </span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink font-heading tracking-tight group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">
            Tips for thriving in our virtual world
          </h3>
        </a>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 7. Comments */}
      <Reveal delay={200} class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink font-heading mb-6">Comments(02)</h3>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          {comments.map((c) => (
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-8 shadow-[var(--shadow-subtle)]">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-ink font-heading">{c.author}</h4>
                <span class="text-xs text-stone">{c.date}</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-steel text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">{c.body}</p>
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-brand hover:underline">
                Reply <Icon name="lucide:corner-down-left" class="w-4 h-4" />
              </a>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      {/* 8. Leave a Reply */}
      <Reveal delay={220}>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-8 md:p-12 shadow-[var(--shadow-subtle)]">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-ink font-heading tracking-tight mb-2">
              Leave a Reply
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-steel">
              Your email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *
            </p>
          </div>

          <form class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <label for="name" class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Name *</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="name"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-full text-ink focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand transition-all"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <label for="email" class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Email*</label>
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-full text-ink focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand transition-all"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <label for="website" class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Website</label>
              <input
                type="url"
                id="website"
                class="w-full px-5 py-3.5 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-full text-ink focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand transition-all"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <label for="comment" class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Comment *</label>
              <textarea
                id="comment"
                rows="6"
                required
                class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-lg text-ink resize-none focus:outline-none focus:border-brand focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand transition-all"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 pt-2">
              <input id="checkbox" type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 rounded border-hairline text-brand focus:ring-brand" />
              <label for="checkbox" class="text-sm text-steel cursor-pointer">
                Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment.
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4">
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-canvas-dark px-8 text-sm font-semibold text-on-dark hover:bg-charcoal transition-colors shadow-[var(--shadow-subtle)]"
              >
                Post comment <Icon name="lucide:send" class="w-4 h-4" />
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
